spatz,<br><br>
I recommend that you read your post of last night. You aren't fooling anyone with your attempt to leave out the incriminating part. <br><br>
As I said, you are transparent. Easy to figure. Everytime you lob one of your softballs it gets knocked out of the park. You get flattened like a pancake every time, thus enabling us to better see through your bullshit.<br><br>
I have come to the conclusion that it is your intense *hatred for yourself* that keeps you coming back for more. Admit it, you once called us baby killers. You much rather would have layed down in front of your fictional train, but instead you defamed young people who answered the call. It is all revealed in your latest posts.<br><br>
I knew another CO who served in WWII. As soon as I was introduced he told me about his tour in Northern Africa as a medic. You, being as ignorant as you are, don't understand why we who served feel the need to talk about our experiences. The CO's are proud of their service.<br><br>
That's the crux of your problem, you never served.<br><br>
Keep up your masochistic efforts, spatz. Students of the war can read them and see for themselves the fact that Veterans WERE abused upon their return home.<br><br>
You are a disgrace to Conscientious Objectors and cause them much harm with your postings to this group.
